name: The Infinite Forbidden - Booster Box
description: Return to where it all began with a new strategy featuring the unstoppable Exodia!

name: Battles of Legend: Terminal Revenge - Booster Box
description: Get awesome foil upgrades as well as sought-after tournament cards in Battles of Legend: Terminal Revenge.

name: 25th Anniversary Rarity Collection II - Booster Box
description: Obtain twice as many Ultra & Secret Rares per pack in the 25th Anniversary Rarity Collection II!

name: Legacy of Destruction - Booster Box
description: Cement your legend as a top-level Duelist with the latest core booster set, Legacy of Destruction!

name: Phantom Knightmare - Booster Box
description: Unlock the terrifying secrets of new themes, find brand-new cards for recent favorites, and meet more memorable monsters!

name: Valiant Smashers - Booster Box
description: Take to the front lines with 3 new themes in Valiant Smashers!

name: The Infinite Forbidden - Booster Pack
description: The Infinite Forbidden contains 100 new cards in all, for a variety of strategies, new and old, including a brand-new World Premiere theme!

name: Battles of Legend: Terminal Revenge - Booster Pack
description: As always with Battles of Legend sets, Battles of Legend: Terminal Revenge will feature a line-up of popular cards getting foil upgrades as well as some popular tournament cards you can use to up your game!

name: 25th Anniversary Rarity Collection II - Booster Pack
description: Whether you're a collector or a competitive Duelist, 25th Anniversary Rarity Collection II is full of cards that everyone will want to get their hands on!

name: Legacy of Destruction - Booster Pack
description: What kind of legacy will you leave? Cement your legend as a top-level Duelist with the latest core booster from the Yu-Gi-Oh! TRADING CARD GAME (TCG), Legacy of Destruction!

name: Scarlet & Violet - Twilight Masquerade Elite Trainer Box
description: The Pokémon TCG: Scarlet & Violet—Twilight Masquerade expansion introduces a world of mischief and mystery, inviting players to explore the land of Kitakami where people and Pokémon live harmoniously with nature.

name: Scarlet & Violet - Temporal Forces Elite Trainer Box
description: Time is on your side with the Scarlet & Violet—Temporal Forces Elite Trainer Box! Put the full force of this expansion in your control with incredible new cards, including awesome Pokémon ex and more.

name: Scarlet & Violet - Paradox Rift Elite Trainer Box
description: Dive into the clouds and explore a land that appears to be unbound by time! With ferocious attacks, Ancient Pokémon like Roaring Moon ex and Sandy Shocks ex appear alongside artificial Future Pokémon like Iron Valiant ex and Iron Hands ex.

name: Charizard ex Premium Collection
description: Charizard ex burns up the opposition's lead with the cunning firepower of a Darkness-type Pokémon!

name: Scarlet & Violet - Twilight Masquerade - Booster Pack
description: A Festival of Mischief & Mystery! Welcome to the land of Kitakami, where people and Pokémon live harmoniously with nature.

name: Sword & Shield - Vivid Voltage - Booster Pack
description: Each Vivid Voltage booster pack contains 10 random cards.

name: Magic the Gathering: Lord of the Rings
description: It's time to take familiar favorites on a whole new adventure! Journey with the characters of Middle-earth and see how they've come to take their place in the newest Magic set.

name: Magic the Gathering: Assassin's Creed
description: The only way to uncover the secrets of the past is to follow in the footsteps of the assassins who came before, and if you've learned anything, it's that you must be swift, precise, and never show your hand.

name: Magic the Gathering: Lord of the Rings - Coolector Booster
description: In secret, Sauron forged a booster—one far more powerful than those owned by Elf, Dwarf, or Man.
